{"tid":119461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟可唔可以用滅火筒噴火人呀？（2）","createTime":"2017-02-13T18:12:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-13T19:01:47.000Z","uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"80f2847a2d3364242d1bebfac71e6c96637602a5","tid":119461,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T18:12:23.000Z","msg":"留名睇罵戰"},{"pid":"badf42ec12db53bd50fbfe33b1bbda5f8d186294","tid":119461,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T18:13:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好多痴撚線留言話唔到最後都唔用滅火筒 我屌你老母 燒多一兩秒已經好大分別 pussy廢up懶有道理 呢d人比火燒 大家記住拎住個滅火筒對住佢 問 你仲o唔ok? 碌多兩碌睇下熄唔到熄到先 未熄到咪住 有件唔會著火既衫com住再睇定d先 咩話 燒爛左塊面？ 等等我睇埋滅火筒係咩類型先 ok 好似唔錯 先生噴得未？ ok我噴喇 一噴 熄左  先生雖然你三級燒傷 但係我救到你條仲命 多謝我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解碌多兩碌會未熜<br />\n點解com住又唔熜<br />\n點解滅火筒噴完唔可以唔熜?<br />\n假膠有返D水準啦<br />\n我都識講啦呢啲<br />\n好多痴撚線留言話要即刻用滅火筒<br />\n我屌你老母<br />\n明明燒一兩秒 碌兩碌就熜<br />\n佢老母一野噴埋黎<br />\n閃都閃唔切<br />\n佢話雖然噴到我凍傷晒<br />\n但係好彩佢救左我<br />\n唔係我就大獲<br />\n我仲諗緊告唔告佢好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n明明有唔傷熄火係要揀個自己有附加傷害既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好以為碌，襟實個人一定無效過滅火筒先得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n請解釋 佐證 舉例說明 當個人著晒火 碌係有效 而且有效過滅火桶 SOURCE係電影定咩? <br />\n<br />\n無防火墊 你係咪打算用淘寶衫幫手?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/12/042434_4b2e07e7256b1e2ef698e15bf18fb839.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F12%2F042434_4b2e07e7256b1e2ef698e15bf18fb839.jpg&h=d4f940f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource係專科書籍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊句有講碌係有效過滅火筒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n碌係3，滅火筒係5，最後選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果係滅火筒有效d，<br />\n佢就調返轉寫如沒有滅火筒，<br />\n可以使用防火墊/滾動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地係講處理救火人既先後次序 唔係講滅火效果既強弱次序<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你都識講先後啦，咁你又跳過前面直接用後面？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有得跳點解唔柒跳? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n處理犯罪要先報警 再等警察黎 有警察係附近仲打咩999 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a89273f0f29d92e34717eaaae970453999e013d","tid":119461,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T18:13:50.000Z","msg":"紀律部隊人員總工會副主席麥錦輝指，當市民看見有人身上著火，應使用大件衣物，如大䄛、毛巾等，直接蓋上傷者身上，「將對方整個包住，再輕輕拍打滅火會比較好。反而用衣物『拂』落去無法滅火之餘，更會令對方受傷，因為他的皮膚表皮已被燒傷，再打落去會更傷害表皮。」至於天熱時，市民身上沒有大件衣物，他表示，亦可使用水瓶作簡單撲滅，並使用地鐵車廂內放置的滅火桶。<br />\n<br />\n無防火墊用大褸毛巾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得自己專業過專業人士我無野好講<img src=